We have tried many different low carb syrups and some have a funny aftertaste...not this brand.By far the best tasting low carb low sugar syrup out there.
Delicious,sugar free syrup.This is my guilt free indulgence.
I was skeptical of a sugar free pancake syrup.As a diabetic I have tried them all but wow I am so happy I gave Walden Farms a try.You really cannot tell its sugar and calorie free.
The syrup is pretty good,but not great.The photo states 6 pack. I thought I was getting a six bottles of syrup.This is one 12 ounce bottle of syrup for $8.61.

Good strong lime taste.Was buying Key West Lime juice but actually like this better for most uses.

I think this a very stupid word requirement.The star rating is the only way I am willing to rate product s.The description rating should be option only.I have hand tremors which requires a lot of corrections.

I would not say there is really anything good about this lime juice.The color is very off putting think urine .It is far too yellow to be taken as true lime juice.The smell of it seems more cleaner like than tangy.I bought it to see if it could replace real limes in ceviche,and,well....it cannot.I will never buy this again.Disgusting.

I am not sure why so many people rated this as high as they have.This has that weird flavor that is similar to those little plastic limes with the lime juice that you get at the grocery store.It has a somewhat limey taste,but that strange flavor negates the lime flavor.I would not use this to substitite for a real lime.
This lime juice fits my needs.It is hard to get fresh limes all the time and this works as well.

These cost $2 at walmart,so I recommend getting these there if you can.The price for these on amazon is quite steep.The product itself is good,and the flavor is what you would expect,with a slight bitterness to it.Very useful as a cooking ingredient or making limeade lemonade .
I am not sure why it is so hard to find large quantities of lime juice...like a 30oz or 40oz.This is very real,good lime juice.

Love it.Great taste too.

Very good product,easy to use,good instructions and great taste.We made 50 lattes frozen blended ,they tasted great and we were able to do them quickly for an event following a church service.

I found this product because I had one given to me at a little local sandwich shop.I loved it.Went online and ordered this bag so I could make them at home.It is delicious.Highly recommend.I am not a fan of chocolate,so vanilla was the go to choice.Husband who is a HUGE fan of chocolate,said he preferred this flavor.Do not be on the fence.Directions are simple its very easy to make!

Thank you very much,I love the Boylan Ginger Ale,I cna t drink any other,since they all have high fructose corn syrup.This is pure and natural,very pleasing!
Enjoy the drinks with the family!!

yummy drinks

Full flavor,no bitterness.Very nice crema foam from Senseo coffee maker.These pods are the most environmentally responsible only thin filter paper discarded.Aluminized plastic bags are totally recyclable.
We bought this for our one cup coffee maker.The flavor is a little on the light side but a very nice blend for general use.
I found this coffee to be a bit bitter for my taste,which is odd because it does not seem to be a very strong very caffeinated cup of coffee.

This makes a good single cup of coffee.Simple to use and easy to clean up.I needed this style for my Hamilton Beach single and or full pot coffee maker which I love.These pods could also be used in a cup of hot water in the manner of a tea bag if you did not have this style single cup maker.
Love my Senseo coffee maker and ordering from Amazon is the only way I can now buy the pods for my morning coffee.So grateful for this opportunity to continue to use this coffee.

When I bought my Senseo coffee machine it was easy to get the pods all over the place.Now I can only find them online.If the prices go higher I will stop buying it but so far Amazon has these for a fair price.Hope they do not disappear altogether!

Still my favorite coffee.Been subscribing for a couple of years now getting four 18 paks every six weeks.So far only two have been defective. the weld on the pod was missed on a area approx 1 8 of an inch and the coffee leaked out during shipment. Amazon replaced it promptly and without any hassle.

I probably cannot tell the difference between good coffee and great coffee.However this coffee meets my taste,is reasonably priced,and extremely easy to use.Takes about 2 minutes from when I put it into the machine and when a hot cup of coffee is ready.It meets my needs.

It is not the tastiest Decaf I have ever had.I always need to put either a Dark Roast or Espresso with it.I would like it much better if it were richer and stronger so that I could just have a completely de caf cup when I want it.
These coffee pods work just right for me.I purchased the dark roast because i like a full flavor coffee and these were not a disappointment to me.I would recommend these to anyone.
I really like this coffee for my Senseo.I believe it is the strongest coffee you can get for this machine.It has a great flavor plus a good strength.Highly recommended.

My mom lives with me and loves a cup of Kona coffee every day.Local grocery store no longer carries the Senseo pods.This is an easy way to order and keep them on hand.When I open my last package,I place my next order and am stocked up in advance.

Great!!I cannot think of anything else except that I am very satisfied with the coffee pods I purchase from you.

happy with product

Price is better than markets.Fewer markets are carrying this system,so selection is diminishing.However,the cost per cup is a fraction of the more prevalent coffee systems,and the coffee is great.So both the vendor and the product is recommended.
Breakfast Blend Coffee Pods are great.The blend is smooth and does not bite.we have been drinking it for years.

These are the best pods I have found.I have tried tons of different ones and none of them compare to senseo French vanilla.

Got a Senseo about 3 years ago and think this is the best coffee available for the least amount of effort.Great fresh coffee with a frothy top on demand and uses simple coffee pods.What else could you want?The Sumatra is excellent.

This is a mild blend.So mild in fact that they even suggest on the box using 2 pads if you want it stronger.I love a strong cup of coffee so this is not for me.Also,do not buy if you want to use this in any other machine.I tried and it does not work.It can not be returned.
Love my Senseo machine and since they stopped selling the coffee pods in supermarkets this is one of the few ways to get the pods.Great coffee.Reasonable price.Highly recommended.
Great tasting coffee and the pods are very convenient as I usually make lousy coffee if I have to measure anything.Very handy having it delivered to my door.

Item as described.This is my favorite coffee.Smooth flavor.No retail place to get this type of coffee pods any more.

the coffee is not that good and the taste is also so,so P.S.I am a vending tech who repairs various coffee machines and as such i taste all brands of coffee and i find this brand lacking.

Its is good my husband loves it He said it taste like real coffee.We will buy it again Thank you

My wife drinks flavored coffee.Me,I prefer what is as close to Birch Bark as you can find.She enjoyed this but found the Vanilla flavoring to be a little to strong for her taste and has settled on Wolfgang Puck French Vanilla,also available from Amazon.So tronger vanilla this is for you,a taste of vanilla try the Wolfgang blend.

I have used these for a while now.Love them.It does take two for each cup of coffee to get taste however.

Great!!!I love the smooth delicious taste of French Vanilla coffee,it is a great way to start my day!!

top quality product.Expensive,but worth the luxury.
